<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>netcoreapp3.1</TargetFramework>
    <ApplicationIcon>Resources\pexels-stas-knop-6616845.ico</ApplicationIcon>
    <ProduceReferenceAssembly>True</ProduceReferenceAssembly>
    <GenerateDocumentationFile>True</GenerateDocumentationFile>
    <SignAssembly>False</SignAssembly>
    <GeneratePackageOnBuild>True</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
    <Title>Calculate ETA</Title>
    <Authors>Enes Okullu</Authors>
    <PackageIcon></PackageIcon>
    <PackageReadmeFile>README.md</PackageReadmeFile>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>Added:
* Adding comments to every lines of code.
* Adding DivideByZeroException to methods when input parameter index is not longer being checkes for it was zero.

Changed:
* CalcETA() and CalcETAUnsafe() methods,  now using nullable parameters.
* CalcETA() methods checks if given parameters are null instead of 0 value.
* CalcETA(..., long tickFrequency) method is now using CalcETA(..., long? frequency)
* avarageElapsedTime varaiable is renamed into avarageElapsedTimeInMs.
* seconds variable is renamed into elapsedSeconds.
* TimeSpanETA() now returns null instead of TimeSpan.Zero when input parameter is null instead of it is zero value.
* TimeSpanETA(), NumberFormatETA(), NameETA(), NameETABetterVisual() now uses new TimeSpan(ticks: ) instead of new TimeSpan(0,0,0,0, milliseconds: (int)eTATimeInMs)

Cancelled:
* NameETA() and NameETABetterVisual() are no longer returning result as $"{etaTimeInMs:0} ms" if input parameters is shorter then a second.</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <Version>1.5.0</Version>
    <Description>CalculateETA is a project to calculate estimated time to arrive on loops whether it is in single-thread or multi-thread applicatons.</Description>
    <Copyright>Okullu</Copyright>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <PackageTags>ETA;Time;LeftTime;Iterations;Multithreading;Singlethread</PackageTags>
    <AssemblyVersion>1.5.0</AssemblyVersion>
    <FileVersion>1.5.0</FileVersion>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://meokullu.github.io/CalculateETA/</PackageProjectUrl>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/meokullu/CalculateETA</RepositoryUrl>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)|$(Platform)'=='Debug|AnyCPU'">
